data.description: Unique cedar log cabin with country living on 3.37 acres within the city limits of Oxford. This adorable gem features 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, a gas log fireplace with a rock exterior, hardwood floors, a tankless hot water heater, and stone countertops in the kitchen. The open floor plan of the living area provides ample room for entertaining and the exquisite hardwood floors make clean-up simple. The spacious living and dining area has beautiful cathedral ceilings and is lit with gorgeous skylights. Outside you will find 3.37 acres of inviting flat land, a charming front porch, a carport, a 20 x 20 workshop with electricity, a storage building, an underground storm shelter, a modern 40 x 40 entertaining/family area with its own gravel driveway, parking area, electricity, outdoor lighting, and the potential for a separate bathroom with the basic plumbing function already completed. This might be the perfect place to add your pool and pool house. Don't miss your opportunity to see it!
